parameters.content:
### 🎯 Purpose  
Formats the translated message for Slack.

### ⚙️ Example (Code node)
```js
const src = $json.source_lang === 'ja' ? '🇯🇵' : '🇺🇸';
const dst = $json.target_lang === 'ja' ? '🇯🇵' : '🇺🇸';
const username = $node["Get File ID"].json.from_username || 'unknown';
const original = $node["Extract Transcript"].json.text || '(no transcript)';
const translated = $node["Translate (OpenAI)"].json.choices[0].message.content || '(no translation)';

const text = `${src} → ${dst} (@${username})\n> ${original}\n\n${translated}`;
return [{ json: { slack_text: text } }];
```

### 🧩 Output  
`slack_text` → sent to next node
